{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"fy","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/fy","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>对于 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a> 元素，此属性用来定义径向渐变的焦点的 y 轴坐标。如果该属性没有被定义，就假定它与中心点是同一位置。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>无</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#coordinate\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#Coordinate\">&lt;coordinate&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>非</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/pservers.html#RadialGradientElementCXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): The radialGradient element</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p></p><dl>\n  <dt id=\"coordinate_2\">&lt;coordinate&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A &lt;coordinate&gt; is a length in the user coordinate system that is the given distance from the origin of the user coordinate system along the relevant axis (the x-axis for X coordinates, the y-axis for Y coordinates). Its syntax is the same as that for <a href=\"#length\">&lt;length&gt;</a>.</p>\n    <p>Within the SVG DOM, a &lt;coordinate&gt; is represented as an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGLength\"><code>SVGLength</code></a> or an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedLength\"><code>SVGAnimatedLength</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html  language-html notran